etzen </b>zu verwenden.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:.05pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",sans-serif\"=\"\">Erwerber der Gastangelkarte <b>Friedfisch / Raubfisch </b>und der <b>Jahreskarte </b>ist es erlaubt <b>toten Köderfisch </b>oder <b>Fischfetzen </b>zu verwenden.</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:.05pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\">Weitere Bestimmungen siehe Anhang!</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0.05pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0.05pt;\"><b>MAXIMAL 2 Edelfische Pro Tag, siehe Bestimmungen!</b></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\r\n</ul></h3>","rules_files":[{"id":580435,"name":"asv-unterharz-e-v-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/157e96943db184f0514944bf24641c7425551b44/asv-unterharz-e-v-bestimmungen.pdf"}],"tickets":[{"name":"Tageskarte Friedfisch - Tageskarte","price":"13,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":1059,"price_id":93255},{"name":"Wochenkarte Friedfisch - Wochenkarte","price":"33,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":1060,"price_id":93256},{"name":"Jahreskarte - Normalpreis inkl. Servicegebühr","price":"165,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":7211,"price_id":93265},{"name":"Wochenkarte Friedfisch & Raubfisch - Normalpreis inkl. Servicegebühr","price":"55,00 EUR","ticket_type_id":7868,"price_id":93270}],"manager":{"id":1469,"name":"ASV Unterharz e. V. ","street":"Am Himmelsgarten 11","postal_code":"06493 ","city":"Harzgerode","telephone":"+4915152368182","email":"striemann@web.de","website":"https://www.harzgerode.de/verzeichnis/mandat.php?mandat=101904&kategorie=118","logo":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/r200x200/1e/05/1e051aa365a4d8a7e26273e970090c39a44f34ca.jpeg","slug":"asv-unterharz-e-v"},"season_begin":"0001-03-01","season_end":"0001-12-31","features":{"accessible":false,"public_transport":true,"boat":false,"belly_boat":false,"digital_ticket":true,"night_fishing":true,"ice_fishing":false,"depth_map":false,"has_gauges"